    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per MRL 2 guidance for Class II devices. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model predicts hemolysis index within experimental uncertainty across the COU operating envelope. Worst-case RH = 0.87 satisfies the RH < 1 regulatory acceptance criterion. The assessment team concludes the model has sufficient credibility for the intended COU of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device.",
